Package: onEyeAirpuff
Title: Corneal Air Puff Pressure Lookup
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("RQ", email = "rq@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Lookup corneal air puff pressure (mmHg) from time after puff onset
    (milliseconds) using split monotonic PCHIP interpolation on digitized
    clinical data.
